      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/sqa-mrl2",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 used under documented QMS with version control, regression test suite, and change-control procedures. Software validation records confirm solver passes all applicable benchmark cases for rotating machinery. Gradation 2 achieved: documented QMS with traceability to solver release notes."
    },
    {
