      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/solver-error-scoped-out",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2, numerical solver error beyond code verification is not required. Iterative convergence monitored via residual reduction to 1e-6 for all equations and confirmed via mass balance error < 0.01%. Round-off error negligible for double-precision computation. Scoped out per MRL 2 requirements with documented justification."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
