      "factorStatus": "scoped-out",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/use-error-scoped-out",
      "rationale": "Simulation workflow executed by a single analyst with 8 years CFD experience in cardiovascular device applications. Workflow documented in a standard operating procedure with peer review of boundary condition setup and post-processing scripts. Scoped out at MRL 2 with documented peer review record as mitigation."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "scoped-out",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/model-form-scoped-out",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on literature consensus for centrifugal pump hemolysis CFD. Power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger) applied with literature coefficients. Model form uncertainty not formally quantified at MRL 2; selection rationale documented. Scoped out per MRL 2 requirements with documented model selection rationale."
